            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced courgette</strong>,<strong> onion wedges</strong>, <strong>tomato wedges</strong>, <strong>peeled garlic</strong>, <strong>free</strong> <strong>range</strong> <strong>chicken thighs</strong>, <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>honey</strong> to a large baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a really good mix up (clean hands is the best way!)</p>",
